maia-kmod: fix kernel 6.4+ API compatibility

- class_create: remove THIS_MODULE arg (removed in 6.4)
- ida_simple_get/remove: replace with ida_alloc_range/ida_free (deprecated in 6.4)
- platform_driver.remove: change return type from int to void (required in 6.11+)

Upstream maia-sdr (including v0.12.0) hasn't updated these APIs yet.

